### Answer a question [POST /role/{role_id}/question/{question_id}/answer]

+ Parameters
    + role_id (required, enum[string]) - User role
        + Members
            + accountant
            + hr
            + accountant_client
            + hr_client
            + business_partner
    + question_id (required, number, `1`)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + answer (Answer)

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Attribute (QuestionAnswered)
